(j) (k) If a trust or estate is permitted an extension to file its income
tax return under IC 6-8.1-6-1, then the return and payment due under
this subsection shall be allowed the same treatment as the extended
income tax return with respect to due dates, interest, and penalties
under IC 6-8.1-6-1.".
